  <title xml:lang="EN">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Samoa First Fiscal &amp; Economic Reform Operation</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1" xml:lang="EN">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The objective of the proposed operation is to support the Government of Samoa&apos;s efforts to strengthen public financial management and facilitate the growth of key sectors of the economy over the medium term. The policy areas under consideration for the proposed operation include: (i) debt management; (ii) procurement; (iii) tax revenue; (iv) payments systems and remittances; (v) tourism/agriculture; and (vi) tackling NCDs.</narrative>
  </description>
